SIMPLE: try_out
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Try out
<hw>Try out</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>to compete for a
postition, as on a sports team or in a theatrical
presentation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Try out</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Try out
<hw>Try out</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to use (something
not previously used) to determine its fitness for a particular purpose;
also, to attempt (a deed) to determine if it will accomplish a
particular purpose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trypsin</ent>⟦br⟧
